content.c_answer2: You can expect to hear plenty of ABBA classics in the show such as 'The Winner Takes It All', 'Take a Chance on Me', 'Knowing Me, Knowing You', 'Dancing Queen', 'Super Trouper', 'Thank You for the Music' and of course 'Mamma Mia'.
